{"tid":646064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"全城中大伏，民主黨同班左膠由頭到尾做左場大龍鳳為許智峯護航！","createTime":"2018-04-28T17:10:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-28T18:34:48.000Z","uid":49388,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1d86f12bc125b382fdb67216224924d63ef4c5cf","tid":646064,"uid":49388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:10:12.000Z","msg":"睇睇享利講乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n【一早講咗爛鴿黨就係做場爛騷，引你班港豬幫佢地包庇許智峯犯刑事罪合理化，你班港豬都仲係要上當】<br />\n<br />\n沒有人比我更認清爛鴿黨的本質，劉慧卿的發言從來只是試水溫，真正的決定權從來都在張李楊集團手中，而他們的決定則是以民粹定奪──即係而家營造咗一堆「撐許」民意，當然亦順理成章轉行包庇路線。<br />\n<br />\n你地成班垃撚圾政論KOL戇撚尻尻瘋狂攻擊老鴿其實就係幫佢地草船借箭，而班本土膠則當正許智峯係烈士看待，證明全部都係無腦任人操控嘅垃撚圾。<br />\n<br />\n民主黨隨風擺柳改變立場，並無改變事件本質：許智峯就係先強搶他人財物，然後再不誠實使用手機盜竊他人私隱，呢個係刑事層級問題，然後你地諗住「向事主及公眾道歉、並承諾會深切反省」就諗住算數？（之但係之前何俊仁又話佢道歉未夠真誠，究竟邊撚個先係代表民主黨、邊撚個只係用黨員身份發言？）<br />\n<br />\n而家黃碧雲執陳澤滔口水尾（我真係高估咗呢個黨嘅水平），話乜撚「民選議員嘅去留，應該係由選民決定」，咁係咪即係民主黨已唔會理調查結果，一定唔會響譴責動議投贊成票？其實呢樣嘢從來無人期望過，重點從來都係，響譴責動議表決期間，你地會唔會避席，定係公然坐響議會入面變相幫手否決議案？係的話，你呢個垃圾黨成班都只不過係偽君子而已<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/010438_880b8a6c3fbd9cd1bb0c7498769e288d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F010438_880b8a6c3fbd9cd1bb0c7498769e288d.png&h=f5c5973a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n點解胡志偉可以響短短兩日間立場轉變咁大，由「民主黨一定會秉公處理，不會有雙重標準，會以與監察政府同樣的規格，甚至更高的要求處理，因為要以身作則，才能有足夠的公信力質疑官員和監察政府。&hellip;&hellip;作為政治組織，大前提是不能包庇成員。」<br />\n<br />\n一轉轉到「看不到搶奪手機應該令許智峯失去議席」？<br />\n<br />\n究竟係「因應民意從善而流」，定係「個劇本一早寫好咗，做場馬蹓戲引你班港豬草船借箭保住議席？」<br />\n<br />\n我望唔透&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/29/010514_757a392a36752094aac875a594c37a91.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F29%2F010514_757a392a36752094aac875a594c37a91.png&h=5fef9f45&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n完～<br />\n<br />\n坦白講，民主黨入中聯辨畀人屌咁多年都WFC , 今日畀人屌三日，三日渣就轉軚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有黃碧雲嗰句&lsquo;至今為止，真正想致許智峯於死地的，恐怕只是建制派&rsquo;，你話今場唔係一場大龍鳳一場話劇我打死都唔信<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3821f4462681d9955ca7f4973aeab8cbfd2502e","tid":646064,"uid":49388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T17:15:49.000Z","msg":"黑臉<br />\n白臉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ac88a49c23c7c7511d3063bec4c3ecb1776cef1","tid":646064,"uid":177047,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:08:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 人地係伏爾泰,我就伏已中"},{"pid":"935e7f9dfaa4d6de5ef430470c636c6892ecb406","tid":646064,"uid":50088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:09:53.000Z","msg":"屌你計贏國之後白鴿黨要做贏黨呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0b56ba616094d42b1a1add02c8d9a0ef381a3f5","tid":646064,"uid":7103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:11:26.000Z","msg":"民主黨邊有咁好權謀手段?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43383f549ba34524751f3deefe1858fb7c02c39a","tid":646064,"uid":6420,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"f0b56ba616094d42b1a1add02c8d9a0ef381a3f5","tid":646064,"uid":7103,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:11:26.000Z","msg":"民主黨邊有咁好權謀手段?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:19:57.000Z","msg":"白鴿識鬼咩<br />\n咪又係收order做野"},{"pid":"6d67c46f8370720775c5517bca78c3ae90b852ca","tid":646064,"uid":74918,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:24:40.000Z","msg":"白鴿無咁醒既<br />\n睇睇呢兩日建制靜晒<br />\n可能係中聯辦出手了"},{"pid":"c7b601bd07a5914139d25986d4704a8a701a20b5","tid":646064,"uid":127988,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:29:19.000Z","msg":"多謝蕭生及時發功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7475fe47470cf9484a04e73ff5727a5ff1c8829f","tid":646064,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-28T18:34:48.000Z","msg":"乜撚嘢都中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}